<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[869,1494,538,819]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[869,1004,538,563]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Comments:</emphasis>
This ectoparasite has been recorded in 
<collectingCountry box="[869,979,570,595]" name="Argentina" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Argentina</collectingCountry>
on bats of the family 
<taxonomicName box="[1252,1435,570,595]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Chordata" rank="family">Vespertilionidae</taxonomicName>
. It is has been recorded in Córdoba and 
<collectingRegion box="[1290,1348,602,627]" country="Argentina" name="Jujuy" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Jujuy</collectingRegion>
on 
<taxonomicName authority="Thomas, 1916" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1916" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="laephotis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Histiotus laephotis</emphasis>
Thomas, 1916
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Garcia, M." box="[1139,1279,634,659]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="579 - 580" refId="ref8786" refString="Garcia, M. 1959. Diptera Pupipara. In: Jornadas Entomoepidemiologicas Argentinas, 1 ª. Buenos Aires, Prensa Medica Argentina. v. 2, p. 579 - 580." type="journal article" year="1959">García, 1959</bibRefCitation>
; Autino 
<emphasis box="[1370,1427,634,659]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">et al.,</emphasis>
1999, 2016); in 
<collectingRegion box="[978,1032,666,691]" country="Argentina" name="Salta" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Salta</collectingRegion>
on 
<taxonomicName authority="(Poeppig, 1835) (Autino et al., 2009)" authorityName="Autino et al." authorityYear="2009" baseAuthorityName="Poeppig" baseAuthorityYear="1835" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="macrotus">
<emphasis box="[1081,1213,666,691]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">H. macrotus</emphasis>
(Poeppig, 1835) (Autino 
<emphasis box="[869,929,698,723]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">et al.,</emphasis>
2009)
</taxonomicName>
; and in 
<collectingRegion box="[1097,1211,698,723]" country="Argentina" name="Corrientes" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Corrientes</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[1273,1493,698,723]" country="Argentina" name="Santiago del Estero" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Santiago del Estero</collectingRegion>
on 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="d'Orbigny &amp; Gervais" baseAuthorityYear="1847" box="[904,1093,730,755]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Eptesicus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="furinalis">
<emphasis box="[904,1093,730,755]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Eptesicus furinalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Garcia, M." box="[1105,1244,730,755]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="579 - 580" refId="ref8786" refString="Garcia, M. 1959. Diptera Pupipara. In: Jornadas Entomoepidemiologicas Argentinas, 1 ª. Buenos Aires, Prensa Medica Argentina. v. 2, p. 579 - 580." type="journal article" year="1959">García, 1959</bibRefCitation>
; Oscherov 
<emphasis box="[1363,1420,730,755]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">et al.,</emphasis>
2012). The identity of the specimen cited as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1916" box="[1303,1431,762,787]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="laephotis">
<emphasis box="[1303,1431,762,787]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">H. laephotis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from Córdoba is doubtful (
<bibRefCitation author="Barquez, R. M." box="[1102,1264,794,819]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="56 - 86" refId="ref7769" refString="Barquez, R. M. 2006. Orden Chiroptera. In: Barquez, R. M.; Diaz, M. M. &amp; Ojeda, R. A. (Eds.). Mamiferos de Argentina. Sistematica y distribuciOn. Mendoza, Sociedad Argentina para el Estudio de los Mamiferos (SAREM). p. 56 - 86." type="book chapter" year="2006">Barquez, 2006</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
